high_descs: Go to the left of the sink
Grab the candle that's to the left of the sink
Back up from the counter and look down at the drawers
Put the candle in the top left drawer
anns.task_desc: Putting a candle in a drawer

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the green vanity on the left.
Pick up the white candle with the gold holder in front of the sink on the counter.
Turn around, walk forward and turn around to face the drawers under the vanity.
Put the candle holder with the candle in the top left drawer and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a candle holder with a candle in a drawer.

high_descs: Head to the sink across the room.
Pick up the candle on the counter.
Move to the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the candle in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a candle in the left drawer under the sink.
